				<td colspan="2"><span>Task: Create and level a bard to 65 without 2-boxing or using other people to PL you (discluding getting buffs in PoK etc...) in the shortest possible time.
<br />

<br />
Gear: You have 500k to equip yourself with.
<br />

<br />

<br />
What race would you choose?
<br />
What equipment will you buy?
<br />
And most importantly, where will you level?
<br />

<br />
I reckon it can be done in less than two days played, although you need to know the game inside and out and be very skillful to do that.
<br />
</span></td>
