				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: hardcore 1-65 without 2-boxing<a name="28307"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 17 04 9:41 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>there's a thread or 2 on ae kiting that you should read.  If you have the cash to dump, get the best droppable instruments you can get I guess, enough HP gear to giggle when 75 mobs stun and beat you up, and line up a jboots mq or a bunch of back packs full of sow pots. BTW you will suck as bard when you hit 65, but I imagine you're prepared to deal with that fact.
<br />

<br />
Not sure if there is a racial penalty for Vah Shir (it seems there may be based on my husband's experience duoing with my halfling cleric, but then halflings do get a +), but I'm sure no other bard race (human half elf or wood elf) has any racial exp mod.  Avoid human for the vision would be my advice.
<br />

<br />
Don't think 2 days played is possible without any assistance at all, honestly, but if anyone could, would be a bard. An experienced bard that knows the spots most likely. I'm leveling a bard on FV and am 30 with like 4 days played, but I'm not hardcore at all.</span></td>
