				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: hardcore 1-65 without 2-boxing<a name="28323"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 17 04 10:15 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Gaccwin: Aye, that is indeed how it sounds like.
<br />
But not everything is what it seems.
<br />

<br />
I have been playing since 1999 on and off. I've gotton 4 chars to 50 pre kunrak, and 5 chars to 65 up until today.
<br />

<br />
I never 2-boxed, and I was never in a guild. I almost never group during weekdays (I go AFK a lot). 
<br />

<br />
So anyway, I now have a 65 monk and 65 wizard. I had a 65 necro, beastlord and shaman.
<br />

<br />
Most of my gear is top of the line bazaar gear.
<br />

<br />
I don't know much about the high end of the game, but I know a lot about leveling and exping. 
<br />

<br />

<br />
And as for the 500k.  I actually have 635K, and I haven't bought it, I saved it.
<br />

<br />
Much like in real life, I save every penny, and I am a very patient bazaar buyer and seller.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
I hope this post doesn't sound like &quot;look how uber I am&quot; because I really don't think as myself as uber. The guys running guilds with 70+ members who are raiding time/GoD daily are surely far more uber than me and doing what they are doing is far harder than what I'm doing.
<br />

<br />
Everytime I make a new char I go to a class board such as this one and ask this question, and every time the answers are 80/20. 80% flames. 20% useful information. 
<br />

<br />
My latest char is my wizard. I made him on August 2003. Got to 65 in five played days (I was slacking, and I forgot to log off one time and was afk for 12 hours bah), and I now have 312 AAs with him and 30 played days.
<br />

<br />
I now want to make a bard. I only played good soloing classes, and a bard they say is one of the best.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

