				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: hardcore 1-65 without 2-boxing<a name="28692"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 18 04 2:05 PM</span></td>
