				<td colspan="2"><span>I do not think that race will really matter. It is my understanding that only halflings get a true xp bonus, with the bard races all being equal.
<br />

<br />
with 500k, I would purchase the following:
<br />

<br />
2x Black Sapphire Electrum Earrings (the 35hp/25mana onesm for ears) ~800 pp total
<br />
Black Sapphire Velium Necklace (65hp/mana neck) ~1200
<br />
Deathmask of the Elysians (12ac, 35 hp face) ~2000-3000
<br />
Cowl of Mortality (haste and hps for head) ~120,000
<br />
2x Velium Fire Wedding Rings (6/65/65 rings) ~600 total
<br />
2x Silver Chitin Wristbands (15 ac and 40 hps) ~16000 total
<br />
Hardened Grey Flesh Sleeves (ac 16 and 25hps arms) ~2000
<br />
Shissar Scaled Gaunts (12 ac 40/40 hands) ~2000
<br />
Matchless Dragonwing Mantle (ac 15 65/65 shoulders) ~30000
<br />
Fungi (chest and regen) ~65000
<br />
Heirophant's Cloak or Greater Pernicity (back) ~14000
<br />
Walrus Fang Belt (50hps) ~5000
<br />
Grey Flesh Pants (35 hps) ~2000
<br />
Barbed Dragonscale Boots (19ac 30hps and sta) ~3000
<br />

<br />
Instruments:
<br />
TDoK ~8000
<br />
LotH ~30000
<br />
McVaxius' Horn of War ~3000
<br />
Flute of Enternal Night ~1200
<br />

<br />
Weapons:
<br />
BDMG ~9000
<br />
Swiftblade of Zek (100hps baby!) ~30000
<br />

<br />
This is about 313k, and will last you till your late 30s/mid 40s.  YOu will now want to swap out some gear.
<br />

<br />
2x Valorian Ring of Gallantry ~16000 total
<br />
Heraldic Armor -- arms and legs -- ~18000 total
<br />
Earring of the Solstice ~4000
<br />

<br />
Use the rest to purchase songs and Ornate Boot Mold ~100000 (at 56)
<br />

<br />
I cannot believe that you can get to 65 in 48 hours played.  I soloed my way to 54 using basically the above equipment and it took me about 2 days played (1-4 newbie zone, 4-16 paludal, 16-40 sol a doing gobbies then gnomes, 40-46 LoIO aqua gobbies, 46-52 TD Raptors, 52-54 ME toilers, 54-61 PoD flys, goos, rats).   
<br />

<br />
For 57-60, it was taking me 6-7 hours per level doing all of the flys.  So going from 57-60 took me about 25 hours alone.  I do not think that stalkers will give any more xp, and they are more limited and contested.  Soloing from 61-64 will take even more as the flys and stalkers will give progressively less xp.  Right now, at 61, I am getting about 12% an hour, so will take me about at least 9 hours barring any deaths to ding 62.  
<br />

<br />
So soloing, I do not think you could get to 65 in under 5 days played.
<br />

<br />
If I had to do it again, I probably would have gone to PoD earlier, at 50-52, and skipped ME.
<br />

<br />
But good luck trying and let us know how you make out.
<br />
</span></td>
